{"id":3002,"date":"2025-06-05T13:38:25","date_gmt":"2025-06-05T06:38:25","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=3002"},"modified":"2025-06-09T10:19:47","modified_gmt":"2025-06-09T03:19:47","slug":"da-mat-bi-noi-man-do","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/da-mat-bi-noi-man-do\/","title":{"rendered":"Da m\u1eb7t b\u1ecb n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0 g\u00ec? D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft v\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y ra"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><b><i>Da m\u1eb7t b\u1ecb n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf <\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">ng\u1ee9a kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1m \u1ea9n v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe l\u00e0n da. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 b\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a n\u00f3. Nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng v\u00e0 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y ra. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 chi ti\u1ebft trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"da-mat-bi-noi-man-do-la-gi\"><\/span><b>Da m\u1eb7t b\u1ecb n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da m\u1eb7t b\u1ecb n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ed3 s\u1ea7n tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da. Th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00e1c n\u1ed1t m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0u h\u1ed3ng ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1ea1t, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng s\u1ebd k\u00e8m theo t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng <\/span><b>da m\u1eb7t b\u1ecb ng\u1ee9a<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">. C\u00e1c n\u1ed1t m\u1ea9n s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111a ph\u1ea7n \u1edf m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 tay ch\u00e2n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dau-hieu-nhan-biet-da-noi-man-do-ngua\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft da n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf ng\u1ee9a<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da m\u1eb7t b\u1ecb ng\u1ee9a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m sao? D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p khi da b\u1ecb n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf ng\u1ee9a:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3752\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3752\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3752\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-1.webp\" alt=\"D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft da n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf ng\u1ee9a\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3752\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u da n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf ng\u1ee9a<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf: N\u1ed1t m\u1ea9n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1ecf nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea7u kim ho\u1eb7c k\u1ebft th\u00e0nh t\u1eebng m\u1ea3ng l\u1edbn, m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ecf th\u1eabm.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ng\u1ee9a ng\u00e1y: M\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ng\u1ee9a c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 dao \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb nh\u1eb9 \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1eef d\u1ed9i, \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn sinh ho\u1ea1t h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u01b0ng t\u1ea5y: M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 v\u00f9ng da b\u1ecb m\u1ea9n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u01b0ng nh\u1eb9 ho\u1eb7c s\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110au r\u00e1t: N\u1ebfu t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u1eb7ng h\u01a1n, da c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111au r\u00e1t, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 khi b\u1ea1n g\u00e3i m\u1ea1nh ho\u1eb7c d\u00f9ng l\u1ef1c ch\u00e0 x\u00e1t.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nguyen-nhan-khien-da-noi-man-do-ngua\"><\/span><b>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn da n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf ng\u1ee9a<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf ng\u1ee9a, bao g\u1ed3m:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ecb \u1ee9ng: Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t, x\u1ea3y ra khi da ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n nh\u01b0:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m: M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m: H\u1ea3i s\u1ea3n, tr\u1ee9ng, s\u1eefa, \u0111\u1eadu ph\u1ed9ng,&#8230; l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thu\u1ed1c: C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i thu\u1ed1c nh\u01b0 kh\u00e1ng sinh (penicillin), gi\u1ea3m \u0111au (aspirin) c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, ph\u1ea5n hoa: Ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m ho\u1eb7c ph\u1ea5n hoa c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3753\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3753\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3753\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-2-2.webp\" alt=\"Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn da n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf ng\u1ee9a\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-2-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-2-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-2-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-2-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3753\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n da n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf ng\u1ee9a<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng <\/span><b>da b\u1ecb ng\u1ee9a n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">: Vi khu\u1ea9n, n\u1ea5m<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">, <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">k\u00fd sinh tr\u00f9ng ( v\u00ed d\u1ee5 demodex) ho\u1eb7c virus x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp l\u00e0m da t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m v\u00e0 n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ec7nh l\u00fd da li\u1ec5u: C\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh l\u00fd nh\u01b0 vi\u00eam da c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ecba, v\u1ea3y n\u1ebfn, \u00e1 s\u1eebng,&#8230; \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n qua t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1: Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef mang thai, sau sinh ho\u1eb7c giai \u0111o\u1ea1n m\u00e3n kinh th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y do r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n hormone.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, stress: Stress k\u00e9o d\u00e0i l\u00e0m suy gi\u1ea3m h\u1ec7 mi\u1ec5n d\u1ecbch, khi\u1ebfn da d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-giam-tinh-dang-da-noi-man-do\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3m t\u00ecnh d\u1ea1ng da n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3754\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3754\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3754\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-3-2.webp\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3m t\u00ecnh d\u1ea1ng da n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-3-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-3-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-3-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-3-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3754\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>C\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3m t\u00ecnh d\u1ea1ng da n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tim-hieu-va-loai-bo-nguyen-nhan-chinh\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Theo d\u00f5i c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 b\u1ea1n ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac trong v\u00f2ng 24-48 gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi da n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ghi ch\u00e9p chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m, \u0111\u1ed3 u\u1ed1ng, m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m, thu\u1ed1c men, m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ed1ng&#8230;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn b\u00e1c s\u0129 da li\u1ec5u \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c x\u00e9t nghi\u1ec7m d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng sau khi \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n, bao g\u1ed3m:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u00e1nh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m g\u00e2y d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0103n th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thay \u0111\u1ed5i lo\u1ea1i thu\u1ed1c n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ap-dung-cac-phuong-phap-xu-ly-tai-nha\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u00c1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p x\u1eed l\u00fd t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9ng kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m: L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m. Thoa kem sau khi t\u1eafm ho\u1eb7c r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef cho da m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf kh\u00f4 ng\u1ee9a.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u00e1nh g\u00e3i: G\u00e3i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m da t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng. H\u00e3y c\u1eaft m\u00f3ng tay ng\u1eafn \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng do v\u00f4 th\u1ee9c g\u00e3i.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3755\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3755\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3755\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-4-2.webp\" alt=\"\u00c1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p x\u1eed l\u00fd t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-4-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-4-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-4-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-4-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3755\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>\u00c1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p x\u1eed l\u00fd t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9: Ch\u1ecdn s\u1eefa t\u1eafm, s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 pH c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng (kho\u1ea3ng 5.5), kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o m\u00e0u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9: Ch\u1ecdn lo\u1ea1i kem kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y b\u00ed da, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"duy-tri-do-am-cho-da-tu-ben-trong\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m cho da t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">U\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee7 n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m v\u00e0 thanh l\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ed9c t\u1ed1, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 da b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf. H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o b\u1ea1n u\u1ed1ng kho\u1ea3ng 2 l\u00edt n\u01b0\u1edbc\/ng\u00e0y, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e9p tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y, tr\u00e0 th\u1ea3o m\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"xay-dung-che-do-an-uong-khoa-hoc\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trong vi\u1ec7c duy tr\u00ec l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh. H\u00e3y:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3756\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3756\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3756 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5.webp\" alt=\"X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3756\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ed5 sung rau xanh v\u00e0 tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y gi\u00e0u vitamin C, E nh\u01b0 cam, b\u01b0\u1edfi, kiwi \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1ng cho da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m cay n\u00f3ng, d\u1ea7u m\u1ee1 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed3 u\u1ed1ng c\u00f3 c\u1ed3n, ch\u1ea5t k\u00edch th\u00edch v\u00ec ch\u00fang c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 b\u00f9ng ph\u00e1t m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ecf.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u01afu ti\u00ean th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m gi\u00e0u Omega-3 nh\u01b0 c\u00e1 h\u1ed3i, h\u1ea1t chia \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng vi\u00eam da.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"kham-suc-khoe-dinh-ky\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00e1m s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef3<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da t\u1eeb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i, b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng n\u00ean kh\u00e1m s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n s\u1edbm c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1m \u1ea9n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0n da nh\u01b0 r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft, d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng,&#8230; \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh c\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u00e0n da \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da m\u1eb7t b\u1ecb n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf. B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch duy tr\u00ec th\u00f3i quen sinh ho\u1ea1t l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh xa c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng. N\u1ebfu <\/span><b>da m\u1eb7t b\u1ecb n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> k\u00e9o d\u00e0i ho\u1eb7c tr\u1edf n\u1eb7ng, \u0111\u1eebng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia da li\u1ec5u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p x\u1eed l\u00fd ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Da m\u1eb7t b\u1ecb n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf ng\u1ee9a kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1m \u1ea9n v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe l\u00e0n da. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 b\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a n\u00f3.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":3751,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-3002","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3002","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3002"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3002\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3980,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3002\/revisions\/3980"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3751"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3002"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=3002"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=3002"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}